targets.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(min("http.request-bytes-sent"), 1s) + non_negative_derivative(min("http.request-bytes-received"), 1s) + non_negative_derivative(min("http.response-bytes-received"), 1s) + non_negative_derivative(min("http.response-bytes-sent"), 1s) AS "total-bytes" from "nom-proxy.server.statistics" where $timeFilter AND "host-name" =~ /^($hostname)$/ group by time($interval), "host-name" fill(null)

SELECT non_negative_derivative(min("tcp.client-bytes-received"), 1s) + non_negative_derivative(min("tcp.client-bytes-sent"), 1s) + non_negative_derivative(min("tcp.server-bytes-received"), 1s) + non_negative_derivative(min("tcp.server-bytes-sent"), 1s) AS "total-bytes" from "nom-proxy.server.statistics" where $timeFilter AND "host-name" =~ /^($hostname)$/ group by time($interval), "host-name" fill(null)
